      <div class="col-md-12"><h2>Tips to remember when you ride your bike...</h2></div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">   
      <div class="col-md-4 columnItem"><h3><%= image_tag("helmet.png", :size => '45x45', alt: "helmet") %><BR>Helmet rule</h3>
        <p class="beta-p">Always wear a helmet that's the right size for you and fitted correctly !</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 columnItem"><h3><%= image_tag("bright.png", :size => '45x45', alt: "wear bright clothes") %><BR>Be bright - be seen</h3>
        <p class="beta-p">Wear something bright or reflective to make sure everyone can see you coming !</p>
      </div>      
      <div class="col-md-4 columnItem"><h3><%= image_tag("route.png", :size => '45x45', alt: "pick a safe route") %><BR>Pick a safe route</h3>
        <p class="beta-p">Plan your cycle journey with your parents, and do your best to stick to cycle paths and quieter roads. If the road looks busy, get off your bike and walk.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
                    
    <div class="row">   
      <div class="col-md-4 columnItem"><h3><%= image_tag("lights.png", :size => '45x45', alt: "use your lights at night") %><BR>Bike lights</h3>
        <p class="beta-p">Fit your bike with reflectors and good strong lights if you're riding in the dark.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 columnItem"><h3><%= image_tag("park.png", :size => '45x45', alt: "be carefull parking your bike") %><BR>Parking your bike</h3>
        <p class="beta-p">Park your bike with thought for other people, use a cycle stand and lock it to something secure !</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 columnItem"><h3><%= image_tag("animals.png", :size => '45x45', alt: "watch out for animals") %><BR>Be careful near animals</h3>
        <p class="beta-p">Give them plenty of room as you cycle past, and don't scare them with your bell !</p>
      </div>
    </div>          
